            throw exception
        }

no, no, no!the whole point of the exceptions (and moreso of the unchecked ones) is to be transparent!if you don't know what to do with an exception do NOT try to handle itthat snippet should just be    return authService.register(registrationRequest.email, registrationRequest.password)
